Update 22 May 2022|
<color=red>Whitelisted login during a DDoS-attack</color>
Due to the fact that a team of bad guys is trying to kill our server with a DDoS attack, whitelist access has been put into effect at this stage. In order to add your IP address to the whitelist, you need to click on #submit-a-ticket and on Create ticket. Send your IP address to the generated ticket. We hope that temporary difficulties will not cause you big troubles. Have a nice game
|https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/954462981670994030/977982193089536080/7217cf124e3b2031.png|https://discord.com/channels/954461476771463170/954509656087203860||
!
Update 20 May 2022|
<color=red>DDoS-attack</color>
Some (censored) people, out of fear of competition, DDoSed our server. We will manage, but we apologize for possible temporary difficulties with the connection. We wish everyone patience and good mood )
